    {
      "id": "graph-ref-focus-failure",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Failure Mode",
      "position": {
        "x": 60,
        "y": 160
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 260,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Failure Mode\n\nIf the host graph-reference surface does not reflect inner focus at all:\n\n- embedded graphs stay visually mute\n- focus continuity breaks\n- the user loses track of what is active inside the fragment\n- graph-reference nodes feel flatter than they should",
        "_classBinding": {
